{
  "id": "adv_event_2209_01_04",
  "title": "初めての\n握手会",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_04-mku001.m4a",
      "text": "……え？\n私が、トリエルの握手会に？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Eh?\nMe‚ at the TRINITYAiLE greeting event?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 5.604671096800001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_04-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "いい案かもしれないわね\n私達アイドルの活動を知る機会にもなるし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It might be a good idea.\nIt could be an opportunity for you to learn about our idol activities.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.8,
      "endTime": 11.149932003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_04-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "バーチャル・シンガーやから勝手が違うかもやけど\n経験積めばその分、表現の幅もきっと広がるやろうし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since you're a virtual singer‚ it might be different‚ but\nWith more experience‚ your range of expression will surely expand.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.3333333333,
      "endTime": 20.1447392782,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_04-mku002.m4a",
      "text": "私、ホログラムだけど出てもいいの？\n準備も必要だし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm a hologram‚ but is it okay for me to participate?\nIt requires some preparation…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.3333333333,
      "endTime": 27.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_04-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ホログラムの準備は、さほど手間ではないよ\nそれに、マジカルミライの宣伝も出来るしな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Preparing a hologram isn't that much of a hassle.\nBesides‚ it's an opportunity to promote Magical Mirai.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.7,
      "endTime": 33.7044672967,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_04-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "助けられてばかりじゃ落ち着かないの\nイベントの宣伝ぐらいは手伝わせて？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't feel comfortable being helped all the time.\nLet us help with the event promotion‚ is it okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.9,
      "endTime": 39.1710655213,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_04-mku003.m4a",
      "text": "みんな……分かった、ありがとう\nそれじゃあぜひ、参加させてもらうね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone… I understand‚ thank you.\nThen‚ I would love to participate.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.3666666667,
      "endTime": 47.306031862800005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_04-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "決まりだね！\n気持ちよくイベントを迎えられるよう作詞も頑張ろう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's decided!\nLet's do our best in preparing the lyrics too!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.5,
      "endTime": 53.064875412,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "おーっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.2666666667,
      "endTime": 54.650521580399996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後　握手会当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Few days later‚ in greeting event",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.9666666667,
      "endTime": 57.8066666286,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 58.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_04-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "山形在住なの？　わあ、遠い所からありがとう！\n地元の人に会えると元気出るよ、えへへ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You live in Yamagata? Wow‚ thank you for coming from such a far place!\nMeeting people from my hometown gives me energy‚ hehe!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59,
      "endTime": 69.0910432816,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 69.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_04-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、今日も来てくれてありがとう～\n君、いつも最前席のチケット取れて、ほんま強運やなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ thank you for coming today~\nYou always manage to get tickets in the front row‚ you're really lucky!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.3,
      "endTime": 78.7180953979,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 78.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_04-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "前にファンレターで、新作グミを教えてくれた人？\nあの時はありがとう！　ずっとお礼を伝えたかったの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The person who told me about the new gummy in the fan letter before?\nThank you for that time! I've always wanted to thank you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.9333333333,
      "endTime": 86.4303853353,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_04-mku004.m4a",
      "text": "これが握手会かぁ……\n本当に、一人一人声を掛けて、握手してるんだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So this is a greeting event…\nYou really shake hands and talk with each person‚ huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.5,
      "endTime": 96.3000452995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 96.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_04-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルは、ファンの応援なくして成り立たないからね\nだからこそ彼女達も、精一杯のお返しをする",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Idols can't exist without their fans' support.\nThat's why they also give their best to repay it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.5,
      "endTime": 103.95696144109999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_04-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "その手段は、歌やパフォーマンスに限らない\n直接会って、言葉で感謝を伝えることも大事なんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The means of repayment aren't limited to singing and performances.\nMeeting directly and conveying gratitude with words is also important.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.1666666667,
      "endTime": 112.13850351980001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 112.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_04-mku005.m4a",
      "text": "直接会って、言葉で感謝を……か\nアイドルって、やっぱりステキな存在だね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Meeting directly and conveying gratitude with words… I see.\nIdols really are wonderful beings‚ aren't they?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.3333333333,
      "endTime": 121.27115643820001,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8833.33333339999
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "ファンA",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fan",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_04-lizfana001.m4a",
      "text": "あの……初音ミクさんとも話して大丈夫なんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um… Is it okay for me to talk to Hatsune Miku-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.5666666667,
      "endTime": 126.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 126.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_04-mku006.m4a",
      "text": "うん！　今日、私はイベントのゲストだから\n来てくれてありがとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! Today‚ I'm a guest at the event.\nThank you for coming.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.8333333333,
      "endTime": 133.40272105530002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 133.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "ファンA",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fan",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_04-lizfana002.m4a",
      "text": "お礼を言いたいのはこっちです！\n私、いつもミクさんの曲に励まされてて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to express my gratitude to you!\nI've always been encouraged by your songs…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.6,
      "endTime": 139.23333333329998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "ファンA",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fan",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_04-lizfana003.m4a",
      "text": "これからも応援してます！　握手……は出来ませんよね\nあはは……頑張って下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll continue to support you! I guess I can't shake hands‚ right?\nAhahaha… Please do your best!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.4333333333,
      "endTime": 149.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 149.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_04-mku007.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう！　頑張るね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you! I'll do my best.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.3,
      "endTime": 151.85233554840002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 153.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_04-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "イベント、大盛況だったね！\nやっぱり握手会って楽しいなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The event was a great success‚ huh!\nGreeting events are always fun.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.1666666667,
      "endTime": 160.7248754184,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_04-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "そうね\nミクは、どうだった？　参加してみて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ they are.\nHow was it for you‚ Miku? Participating in it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.9333333333,
      "endTime": 165.0668480237,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 165.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_04-mku008.m4a",
      "text": "うん、楽しかったよ\n誘ってくれて、ありがとう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ it was fun.\nThank you for inviting me!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.2666666667,
      "endTime": 170.5821767488,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_04-mku009.m4a",
      "text": "あんな風にファンと触れ合える様子って\n見ていて凄く新鮮だったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Seeing the interaction with fans like that\nwas really refreshing.",
        "id": ""
